      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIVER BEAUTY (7) turned in a better effort last start over this track and trip and gets a slight gear change to help keep her on course. The inside draw this time looks a big tick for her and if she can run up to her most recent figure, she'll be hard to hold out. REINCARNATED (4) wasn't far away on debut last start over 1200m at York, finishing fifth and beaten 4 lengths. Open to sharp improvement and can get off the mark this time. CORNERBACK (1) resumes from a spell of four months. Could only manage to finish sixth at the latest run over 1600m at Strathalbyn. Rates highly and is a chance to break through. THE SESSIONE (3) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1200m at this track when finishing eighth. Nicely placed to find some form. SO I THOUGHT (6) is in the mix.",
